{"id":672277,"date":"2022-11-18T17:00:00","date_gmt":"2022-11-18T11:30:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/?p=672277"},"modified":"2025-09-03T15:42:16","modified_gmt":"2025-09-03T10:12:16","slug":"top-career-options-after-ma-in-journalism-mass-communication","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/top-career-options-after-ma-in-journalism-mass-communication","title":{"rendered":"Top career options after MA in Journalism &amp; Mass Communication"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>A <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/master-of-arts-in-journalism-mass-communication\">Master&#8217;s in Journalism and Mass Communication<\/a> (JMC) is a two-year postgraduate course that is designed to prepare students for careers in media, journalism and communication. Aspiring journalists who have completed their graduation can opt for this course to get trained in various techniques of reporting, writing, editing and broadcasting.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>After completing the MA JMC course successfully and getting good grades, you can move on to pursue higher studies like doctoral programs, or take up roles as an editor at a newspaper or magazine or even start your own publishing company.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/blogs\/journalism-and-mass-communication-as-a-career-in-india\">Journalism and Mass Communication as a career in India<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-why-should-you-do-a-master-s-in-journalism-and-mass-communication\"><strong>Why should you do a master&#8217;s in journalism and mass communication?<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>There are many reasons why you should pursue a master&#8217;s degree in this field. One of them is that getting a master&#8217;s degree will help you get better mass communication jobs and also improve your chances of getting into top companies. If you want to be a successful journalist or editor, then it is important that you have the best education possible so that you can be competitive with other potential candidates.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the reasons why you should pursue a master&#8217;s degree in journalism is that it will help you get better job opportunities in mass communication. You may be able to find some entry-level positions with only an undergraduate degree, but if you want to go far in this field, then getting a master&#8217;s degree is absolutely essential.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-high-paying-job-roles-for-ma-jmc-aspirants\"><strong>High-paying job roles for MA JMC aspirants<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In today&#8217;s competitive world, most employers and recruiters want to hire people with advanced degrees. Let&#8217;s check some mass communication and journalism career options:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Director of communications<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>There are many career options for you after MA JMC. One of the best ones is the role of Director of Communications, which entails managing communication strategies and campaigns. The average salary of a Director of Communications is around <a href=\"https:\/\/www.ambitionbox.com\/profile\/director-communications-salary\">\u20b9 32.5 LPA<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Public relations manager<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>A public relations manager is responsible for maintaining good relationships with the media, companies, and other organizations. They also give advice on how to manage situations that will impact their company&#8217;s reputation. A successful public relations officer must also be able to think strategically about how information can be used to benefit their organization in the long term. The average salary of a Public relations manager is around <a href=\"https:\/\/www.ambitionbox.com\/profile\/pr-manager-salary\">INR 7.5 LPA<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Media planner<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>A media planner can be a part of an advertising agency or marketing firm and get paid to come up with a strategy based on the client&#8217;s brief. They need to understand the client&#8217;s business objectives and then work out how best to achieve them through different media channels such as TV, print, radio etc. The average salary of a Media planner is around INR<a href=\"https:\/\/www.ambitionbox.com\/profile\/media-planner-salary\"> 4.2 LPA<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Social media manager<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Social media managers are responsible for creating and maintaining a company&#8217;s social media presence. They can work with the creative team to develop a company&#8217;s social media strategy and identify which platforms are best for reaching their audience. They are also responsible for measuring the success of this strategy by analyzing metrics such as engagement, impressions, and click-through rates. The average salary of a Social media manager in India is around <a href=\"https:\/\/in.talent.com\/salary?job=social+media+manager\">INR 4.8 LPA<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>TV producer<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>A TV producer is responsible for the production of television programs. They manage budgets and timelines, and they hire writers, directors and actors to work on their shows. They work with the channel to market the show as well as distribute it. The average salary of a TV producer is around <a href=\"https:\/\/www.payscale.com\/research\/IN\/Job=Film%2FTV_Producer\/Salary\">INR 9.5 LPA<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Filmmaker<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>As a filmmaker, you will be required to create content for television and digital media. You will also be required to make advertisements that are visually appealing and persuasive in nature. As a filmmaker, you need to have creativity, a good understanding of the audience and also the ability to work under pressure. The average salary of a Filmmaker is around <a href=\"https:\/\/www.ambitionbox.com\/profile\/film-maker-salary\">INR 4.2 LPA<\/a>.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Event manager<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Event managers are responsible for planning and organizing events. They manage budgets, resources, and vendors to ensure that their clients&#8217; events go off without a hitch. Event managers set up venues and catering options; coordinate with volunteers; handle logistics such as transportation, security, and parking; work with sponsors to attract attendees, and manage the event timeline. The average salary of an Event manager is around INR <a href=\"https:\/\/www.ambitionbox.com\/profile\/event-manager-salary\">4.0 LPA<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Digital Marketer<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Digital marketing is the process of promoting a product or service using digital channels and technologies, such as social media, search engine optimization and e-commerce. Digital marketers use a variety of tools and techniques to accomplish their goals.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;ve got excellent communication skills, leadership qualities and keen business acumen paired with a passion for innovation, then this could be the right career option for you. The average salary of a Digital Marketer is around<a href=\"https:\/\/www.ambitionbox.com\/profile\/digital-marketing-manager-salary\"> INR 7.2 LPA<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Secure a top-paying job with an online MA JMC from Manipal University Jaipur<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can secure a top-paying job with an <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/master-of-arts-in-journalism-mass-communication\">online MA JMC<\/a> from Manipal University Jaipur, through <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/\">Online Manipal<\/a>. This university is the oldest journalism school in India and has a good reputation for its journalism courses. In fact, most of the students get placed in top media organizations after completing their courses at MUJ. So if you want to pursue your career as a journalist or even become an anchor person or scriptwriter, then this is the right place for you!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>A Master&#8217;s in Journalism and Mass Communication (JMC) is a two-year postgraduate course that is designed to prepare students for careers in media, journalism and communication. Aspiring journalists who have completed their graduation can opt for this course to get trained in various techniques of reporting, writing, editing and broadcasting. After completing the MA JMC [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":19,"featured_media":669227,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[610],"tags":[19,53],"class_list":["post-672277","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-master-of-arts","tag-online-degree","tag-online-majmc"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v27.5 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/product\/yoast-seo-wordpress\/ -->\n<title>Top career options after MA in Journalism &amp; Mass Communication - Online Manipal<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"If you&#039;ve completed your MA in Journalism and Mass Communication, then here are some top job roles you can explore.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/672277\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"